3. Magic number. if you add sum of digits which results in 1, then it is magic number. 
    example: 19 is magic number.
            19 → 1 + 9 = 10
            10 → 1 + 0 = 1  

    public static boolean isMagic(int num) {
        while (num > 9) {
            int sum = 0;
            while (num > 0) {
                sum += num % 10;
                num /= 10;
            }
            num = sum;
        }
        return num == 1;
        }


